{"tid":2380212,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"210125 深水埗成個街區要強制檢測？ - 每日監察衞生署強制檢測名單有冇出錯","createTime":"2021-01-25T17:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T21:37:23.000Z","uid":51754,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0e3c591b9de578a9fc456f02e9460104678029cb","tid":2380212,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:11:38.000Z","msg":"前文提要: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2349363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2349363</a><br />\n可以先入去睇睇 #1<br />\n--------------<br />\n<strong>衞生署錯得5+2次，再有出錯絕對唔出奇</strong><br />\n曾出錯大廈包括：<br />\n屯門康利中心<br />\n將軍澳翠林邨安林樓 青衣青華苑華欣閣 秀茂坪曉麗苑曉星閣<br />\n葵涌華豐園<br />\n富榮花園2座 (01/17；最後喺01/21都符合咗準則上榜）<br />\n將軍澳君傲灣3座<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>所以嚟緊每日都會監察衞生署強制檢測名單有冇出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每日一post更新強制檢測名單資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[每日不定時更新]</strong> 強制檢測名單追蹤調查<br />\nGoogle Docs <strong><span class=\"large\">一表睇晒衞生署有冇老屈強制檢測</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/168Sb1uJDl2_pWTzUNKHd5FDh8fsSzUcNDmFSoXnstog/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F168Sb1uJDl2_pWTzUNKHd5FDh8fsSzUcNDmFSoXnstog%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=1126e45d\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/168Sb1uJDl2_pWTzUNKHd5FDh8fsSzUcNDmFSoXnstog/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>第一批名單入面，已經發現有3至8座大廈都好可能係被錯誤列入名單</strong></span></span><br />\n即使呢批大廈已經完咗強制檢測都好，我哋都唔會忘記衞生署錯漏百出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例子 (第一批完整資料可參考google docs/第1個post):<br />\n<strong>1. 「過去14日」定義？</strong><br />\n蘇屋邨櫻桃樓 <strong>12/16</strong> #7724 有源頭 12/28 #8637 源頭不明<br />\n昌運中心華昌閣 <strong>12/16</strong> #7751 源頭不明 12/18 #7954 有源頭<br />\n呢個論點係鄭松泰首先提出，<strong>「過去14日」應該只包括公佈當日起倒數14日</strong><br />\n例如12/30計，係唔應該包括12/16，只應該計12/17 ~ 12/30<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 冇返過屋企都計佢棟樓中獎？</strong><br />\n順天邨天權樓 12/17 #7850 公佈確診，有源頭<br />\n12/26 #8540 確診，被列入聯合醫院群組，已死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12/16 晚 #8540 入聯合，情況持續惡化，12/26 公佈確診，12/28 凌晨 1 時 19 分離世<br />\n#8540 明顯係入到聯合先被傳染，期間都冇返過屋企<br />\n而聯合個超級傳播者都已經搵到出嚟 (#8376 屬「本地個案」)<br />\n如果以上資料全部屬實，即係只有一個單位出事，絕不符合12/30 針對源頭不明個案新準則<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 兩公婆同一個單位都要檢？</strong><br />\n美城苑貴城閣 <em>12/15 #7654 有源頭</em><br />\n12/18 #7953 有源頭 , #7955 源頭不明，根據區議員資料，呢兩單係夫婦，即同一個單位<br />\n12/15呢單唔符合「過去14日」定義，咁就得一個單位有兩公婆中，<br />\n邊度符合兩個單位+其中一個冇源頭嘅定義？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>4. 兩單都有源頭都要檢？篤數唔好篤得咁過份！</strong><br />\n葵涌荔景山路華豐園 <em>12/15 #7635 源頭不明</em><br />\n12/18 #7938 有源頭<br />\n12/28 #8633 有源頭，係聯合醫院職員，已被列入聯合醫院群組<br />\n12/15呢單唔符合「過去14日」定義，即係<strong>得兩個單位有兩個各自有源頭個案，</strong><br />\n完全唔符合強制檢測準則！<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>01/04 衞生署承認#7635及#7938住址為「觀塘華峰園」，並不是「葵涌華豐園」，不會在「葵涌華豐園」執法檢查強制檢測結果。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>強制檢測標準</ins> 如果有錯麻煩幫手指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12/10 「一大廈有四單位不相識確診須強檢」<br />\n// 如果大廈有4個不相識的單位有確診個案，就要強制檢測，但亦要看情況，包括環境污染及風險評估等，因此並非硬指標 //<br />\n12/30 針對源頭不明個案新準則<br />\n// 大廈兩周內有兩個單位有確診、其中最少一個單位屬源頭不明，全幢大廈居民要強制檢測 //<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418354\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418354&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=66b89e48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418354&h=a1b31ff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418354</a><br />\n(即係如果兩個單位都係有源頭，就唔屬於強制檢測範圍)<br />\n(但係最新用字係兩個或以上單位出現無關連確診個案)<br />\n其他 // <strong><span class=\"x-large\">一句到尾，個龍門任佢搬</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />//<br />\n<br />\n<ins>備註</ins><br />\n由於<strong>衞生署由第三波疫情開始唔會再公佈具體流行病學關連</strong>，只有10個人或以上先會計入「群組」。<br />\n因此，除非有其他消息來源指明，否則我哋係唔會知道個案係唔係來自同一單位，<strong>多撚謝衞生署</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>呢個post同google docs會盡可能每日更新<br />\n直到冇大廈再要做強制檢測為止</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">睇完記得幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你好彩唔使強制檢測，但香港仲有數以萬計香港人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至今為止仲未有傳媒跟進報導5+1座大廈以外其他懷疑出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n但即使未必真係能夠令衞生署認真檢視錯誤都好<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><strong>我哋都唔可以任得個政府習非成是</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>資料來源</ins><br />\n武漢肺炎民間資訊 <a href=\"https://wars.vote4.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwars.vote4.hk%2F&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=2b2e900f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wars.vote4.hk/</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://wars.vote4.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwars.vote4.hk&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=b422e1f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">wars.vote4.hk</a> 要人啊！ - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2348322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2348322</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎個案的最新情況 - 衞生署衞生防護中心<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/local_situation_covid19_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2Flocal_situation_covid19_tc.pdf&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=07bf72c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/local_situation_covid19_tc.pdf</a> <br />\n各區區議員(Google Docs同民間資訊都有link)"},{"pid":"813d7d52114551730c1601b217127e7e0b453543","tid":2380212,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2649fa7708cb58a3e2c11dba890a1ba349524ae3","tid":2380212,"uid":128558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40eb5a9bf737bb59d9cf998cbb384009a91a5288","tid":2380212,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af6f679db99ec27674bdfc9cc26fbb3e89ebfdf","tid":2380212,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84f85e98540f41fb9149635f5f6a8a9553b07b1","tid":2380212,"uid":51754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:39:23.000Z","msg":"210125 有21座大廈上榜<br />\n1座北角 + 1座油麻地碧街<br />\n+ 19座深水埗<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">其中17座都來自同一街區</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">長沙灣道/南昌街/鴨寮街/北河街範圍內所有大廈<br />\n均已先後被列入強制檢測</span></span></strong></p><br />\n<br />\n佐敦西北 <strong>是日冇大廈上榜</strong><br />\n<br />\n01/22 有一座懷疑出錯：<br />\n<strong>九龍油麻地炮台街66至70號啟儀閣</strong><br />\n01/22 &gt; 9921<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">符合要驗準則，晏晝宣佈完要驗，但夜晚刊憲又唔列出</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n01/19 有一座懷疑出錯：<br />\n<strong>九龍油尖旺偉晴街 14-42 號偉晴閣 A 座及 B 座</strong><br />\n01/19 &gt; 9711 , 9718<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">根據政府資料，兩個都係偉晴閣 A 座，咁到底B座點解都要強制檢測？</span></strong><br />\n<strong>琴日有巴打報料，就話兩座只有二樓係相連</strong><br />\n<br />\nNew Brooklyn aka 深水埗<br />\n九龍深水埗汝州街 280-286 號永泰樓<br />\n01/25 &gt; 10132<br />\n九龍深水埗汝州街 171-173 號<br />\n01/25 &gt; 10151<br />\n<br />\n另外長沙灣道/南昌街/鴨寮街/北河街 街區全面中榜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GokBjcM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGokBjcM.png&h=e3837850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南方樓確診完仲有+ve 要驗都叫理解到<br />\n<strong>但其餘大廈真係十幾棟樓一齊+ve 咁巧合？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n推測可能：<br />\n1. 污水樣本以街區以單位抽驗<br />\n2. 採樣到化驗到公佈中間有出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 深水埗已經成為佐敦2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. <strong>Why not BOTH?</strong><br />\n<br />\n01/19 有一座懷疑出錯:<br />\n九龍深水埗欽州街 56 號明輝大廈<br />\n01/05 &gt; 9038<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">又係「過去14日」定義問題，究竟咩叫「過去14日內」？<br />\n1月5號都算係過去14日？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔關社區強制檢測事:<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><em>(?) - 無源頭 (R) - 有源頭</em></span><br />\n<br />\n香港北角錦屏街 37-43A 號東發大廈 C 座<br />\n01/18 &gt; 9665(?) , 01/20 &gt; 9738(R)<br />\n01/25 &gt; 10147(?)<br />\n同層兩個單位<br />\n<br />\n九龍油麻地碧街15-27A號<br />\n<strong>二次檢測，污水樣本檢測持續呈陽性</strong><br />\n<strong>封區大熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">【仁石樓二次檢測跟進】</span></span></strong><br />\n今日再睇多次當區區議員尹兆堅個專頁，<br />\n<strong>清楚指明屋邨管理諮詢委員會群組有消息指出，仁石樓有新嘅懷疑確診個案。</strong><br />\n但至今仍未有仁石樓新個案正式公佈<br />\n聽日會再繼續留意最新消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AndrewWanbulletin/posts/5248605798482763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAndrewWanbulletin%2Fposts%2F5248605798482763&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=8550f23e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AndrewWanbulletin/posts/5248605798482763</a><br />\n如果有記者朋友睇到，幫手問問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n01/24 二次檢測<br />\n葵涌梨木道120號石蔭邨仁石樓<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">二次檢測，原因不明</span></span></strong><br />\n01/16 &gt; 9484(?) , 01/17 &gt; 9530(R) , 01/17 &gt; 9555(R)<br />\n<br />\n01/14 首次強檢是因三個同屬09室座向的單位出現確診個案<br />\n相關個案已被列入仁石樓09室群組<br />\n以上三宗個案未被列入，是否同單位，<br />\n<br />\n「考慮到病毒潛伏期有機會較長，因此有關人士須進行第二次檢測。」<br />\n(政府就強制檢測公告刊憲，01/24)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202101/24/P2021012400766.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202101%2F24%2FP2021012400766.htm&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=b1bdc705\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202101/24/P2021012400766.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n當區區議員尹兆堅批評<strong><span class=\"red\">政府未有徹查當中有何傳播關連，便再做強制檢測，做法擾民。</span></strong><br />\n十日兩檢玩謝仁石樓居民 (蘋果日報)<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/V42GEXC74JANBI2C3OVQEMXYQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FV42GEXC74JANBI2C3OVQEMXYQQ%2F&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=dcd9a255\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FV42GEXC74JANBI2C3OVQEMXYQQ%2F&h=bf15ad18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/V42GEXC74JANBI2C3OVQEMXYQQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n估計有機會係因為屎渠出現過倒灌+都有非09住戶中招<br />\n<strong>但4:30記者會同政府新聞公報都冇指明原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅區議員：【石蔭區資訊-仁石樓倒湧問題解決】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AndrewWanbulletin/posts/5229348020408541\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAndrewWanbulletin%2Fposts%2F5229348020408541&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=2ad20737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AndrewWanbulletin/posts/5229348020408541</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>01/22 確定出錯</strong><br />\n新界將軍澳君傲灣3座<br />\n01/22 &gt; 9883(?)<br />\n14日內得一單，不符合準則<br />\n晏晝宣佈要驗，夜晚刊憲冇列出<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">01/21 疑似出錯:<br />\n新界葵涌安足街 7 號安蔭邨德蔭樓<br />\n呢棟係符合準則，但資料有誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n單位 1 及 2 (不同樓層 互不相識)<br />\n01/08 &gt; 9135(?) , 01/12 &gt; 9287(R) , 9289(R)<br />\n01/16 &gt; 9457(R)<br />\n<br />\n單位 3<br />\n01/21 &gt; 9842(R) , 9843(?)<br />\n01/21 &gt; 9858(R)<br />\n三個單位全屬不同層數及座向<br />\n因未能準確辨識單位1及2之個案，故不分別列出所屬單位1/2<br />\n<br />\n<strong>4:30記者會就話「單位2」係01/14起發病，但根據紀錄 #9457 係無病徵<br />\n而如果 #9457 同最早三單唔係同一個單位<br />\n即係德蔭樓01/16時已經符合強制檢測準則</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係衞生署又柒撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以上由張竹君公佈資料一定有嘢錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">真係符合準則就遲幾日先話驗<br />\n唔係咁符合又成日老屈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">01/20 疑似出錯:<br />\n九龍渡船角文蔚街 25-47 號文耀樓</span></strong><br />\n01/17 &gt; 9684(R)中座<br />\n01/20 &gt; 9760(?)前座<br />\n<strong><span class=\"green\">01/20 冇出錯:<br />\n香港鰂魚涌康安街 14-16 號康怡花園 N1 座</span></strong><br />\n01/15 &gt; 9444(?) , 01/16 &gt; 9482(R) , 01/17 &gt; 9540(R)<br />\n01/20 &gt; 9793(?)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">康怡就識分N1N2座(兩棟樓不過共用管理員等等管理安排)<br />\n八文樓就唔識分前中後座(出入口等設施都係唔相連)，咩玩法？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>社區強制檢測</ins></strong> <em>aka 「小區強制檢測」</em><br />\n為咗所謂「小區清零」，衞生署話個範圍入面嘅大廈有一個單位中都要強制檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時有兩區中獎：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>佐敦西北</strong><br />\n範圍：彌敦道、佐敦道、渡船街、甘肅街，呢四條街圍住嘅所有樓。<br />\n<br />\n01/06 ~ 01/19 期間逗留以下「核心區域」超過兩個鐘人士<br />\n要喺01/22 或之前 被檢測， 01/15 ~ 01/19 已被檢測就唔使再做:<br />\n新填地街1-65號 , 廟街148-184A號 , 北海街、廟街、寧波街及新填地街範圍內<br />\n<br />\n<del>Sham Shui Po is the</del><br />\n<strong>New Brooklyn</strong><br />\n範圍：大埔道、楓樹街、界限街、荔枝角道、欽州街呢五條街圍住嘅所有樓。<br />\n<br />\n個案詳情可以去 google drive / <a href=\"http://WARS.VOTE4.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FWARS.VOTE4.HK&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=576f5aa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">WARS.VOTE4.HK</a> 睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>過往資料</strong><br />\n<br />\n210124 新增 4 座大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gANtRT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gANtRT</a> <strong><span class=\"red\">仁石樓二次檢測原因不清</span></strong><br />\n210123 新增 6 座大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gANtRT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gANtRT</a><br />\n210122 新增 9 座大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gAFCxT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gAFCxT</a> <strong><span class=\"red\">是日衞生署疑似出錯</span></strong><br />\n210121 新增 10 座大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gAymmT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gAymmT</a> <strong><span class=\"red\">是日衞生署疑似出錯</span></strong><br />\n210120 新增 12 座大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gAihkT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gAihkT</a> <strong><span class=\"red\">是日衞生署疑似出錯</span></strong><br />\n210119 新增 11 座大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gAihkT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gAihkT</a> <strong><span class=\"red\">是日衞生署疑似出錯</span></strong><br />\n210118 新增 7 座大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gAbpdT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gAbpdT</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[每日不定時更新] 強制檢測名單追蹤調查<br />\nGoogle Docs 一表睇晒衞生署有冇老屈強制檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/168Sb1uJDl2_pWTzUNKHd5FDh8fsSzUcNDmFSoXnstog/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F168Sb1uJDl2_pWTzUNKHd5FDh8fsSzUcNDmFSoXnstog%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=1126e45d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/168Sb1uJDl2_pWTzUNKHd5FDh8fsSzUcNDmFSoXnstog/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"9f3ada7ca2b6e0ccb1693258bcc3549255ad8dc9","tid":2380212,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:39:33.000Z","msg":"---------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong>For 不幸中咗強制檢測名單嘅手足</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">流動採樣站同社區檢測中心都係撩口撩鼻，外判俾中資公司負責居多</span><br />\n<br />\n樽仔(三)係自己起身吐口水，同埋普通科門診，係咩機構負責待查<br />\n但以往有「承辦商」運送樣本 / 檢測 / 出SMS 過程中犯錯嘅新聞<br />\n即係都有機會係外判俾中資公司做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果你唔想俾錢，呢個已經係相對好少少嘅途徑<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果你能夠俾錢做，不妨跟名單搵私人機構做<br />\n但係要留意，當中都有好多係中資機構<br />\n同埋唔係間間都出到SMS，最好問清楚相關機構先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>受檢人士可選擇以下檢測途徑：<br />\n<span class=\"small\">（一）於流動採樣站接受檢測服務（名單及服務對象（如適用）<a href=\"http://見www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%A6%8Bwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=e45c7913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">見www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a> ）；<br />\n（二）於社區檢測中心接受檢測服務（<a href=\"http://名單見www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E8%A6%8Bwww.communitytest.gov.hk%2Fzh-HK%2F&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=41a06584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">名單見www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/</a> ）；<br />\n（三）於121間郵政局、20個港鐵站設置的自動派發機或醫院管理局（醫管局）47間指定普通科門診診所索取深喉唾液測試樣本收集包，並把樣本交回指定樣本收集點（派發點及時間，<a href=\"http://以及樣本收集點及時間見www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E9%BB%9E%E5%8F%8A%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E8%A6%8Bwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=cbd65486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">以及樣本收集點及時間見www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a> ）；<br />\n（四）於醫管局普通科門診診所按照醫管局醫護人員的指示接受檢測；<br />\n（五）自行安排接受由衞生署認可，並可就檢測結果發出電話短訊通知的私營化驗所提供的檢測（<a href=\"http://名單見www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E8%A6%8Bwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2FList_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=b71c629b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">名單見www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf</a> ）；或<br />\n（六）使用衞生防護中心派發到相關指明地方的樣本瓶（如適用），並按有關指示交回已採樣本的檢測樣本收集瓶。</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1d8a37554fc7890a68c2b2fd88c92f74320e45a7","tid":2380212,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"政府分批強搶 dna 丫嘛"},{"pid":"671dba51f168fcc5e63589712aac08999d72c6da","tid":2380212,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2649fa7708cb58a3e2c11dba890a1ba349524ae3","tid":2380212,"uid":128558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:41:34.000Z","msg":"豪仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁夜仲唔訓 辛苦晒<br />\n<br />\n長沙灣道/南昌街/鴨寮街/北河街 成個街區都有份要驗<br />\n有冇辦法幫大家了解多少少詳細情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdcb4e416d532df029ffd66e0f8be27016527cff","tid":2380212,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:47:26.000Z","msg":"成個街區強制檢驗？<br />\n油麻地爆到七彩反而無咩動作"},{"pid":"fe7fd60153b5716d2617fdc6e21dcc63fdaf2727","tid":2380212,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdcb4e416d532df029ffd66e0f8be27016527cff","tid":2380212,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:47:26.000Z","msg":"成個街區強制檢驗？<br />\n油麻地爆到七彩反而無咩動作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:50:07.000Z","msg":"油麻地肯定係有輘輷<br />\n成條東安街碧街爆晒<br />\n<br />\n合理做法係要搵人上門檢驗單位<br />\n唔可以再俾市民住同出入呢啲有問題大廈"},{"pid":"aeef5d3dc31c9b8396d6ca7e6125004c3c4c2f3b","tid":2380212,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:01:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee2c2475e9bbc116079c5b16e957c84f8d55677","tid":2380212,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdcb4e416d532df029ffd66e0f8be27016527cff","tid":2380212,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T17:47:26.000Z","msg":"成個街區強制檢驗？<br />\n油麻地爆到七彩反而無咩動作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:07:18.000Z","msg":"鎖港...<br />\n「軍事」「香港」「漫畫多圖」《最終解決方案》[2]<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fJAmGS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fJAmGS</a>"},{"pid":"dab7ec573f142a6958f4699af481b6e0dba1c9bc","tid":2380212,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T19:33:49.000Z","msg":"01/26 03:33<br />\n<strong>初步懷疑係成個街區求其抽街頭街尾就當驗晒咁多棟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝民協何啟明(唔係做副焗腸嗰條柒碌)深夜三點仲出post跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n// 新聞一出，深水埗街坊會FB Group嘅街坊同連登嘅網友都質疑化驗準確程度，因為都見到部份抽水辦嘅人員只係係街頭街尾抽驗，究竟政府點驗大家都唔知，之後驗完出嚟有事，其實搞唔清係邊座，於是就成堆大廈都要驗，我地聽日就會聯絡政府部門問清楚情況。 //<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kalvinhokaiming/posts/1882599121887450\